us.ihmc.euclid.referenceFrame.interfaces

Interface FrameOrientation2DBasics

  • All Superinterfaces:
    us.ihmc.euclid.interfaces.Clearable, FixedFrameOrientation2DBasics, FrameChangeable, FrameOrientation2DReadOnly, Orientation2DBasics, Orientation2DReadOnly, ReferenceFrameHolder, us.ihmc.euclid.interfaces.Transformable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FrameOrientation2D

    public interface FrameOrientation2DBasics
extends FixedFrameOrientation2DBasics, FrameChangeable
    Write and read interface for a 2D orientation that is expressed in a mutable reference frame.

    A 2D orientation is in the XY-plane, i.e. the yaw angle about the z-axis.
